  "detailed_description": "This video details the comprehensive remediation of a child's bedroom severely infested with black mold. The process begins by revealing the hidden mold behind furniture and highlighting the health issues suffered by the child due to mold exposure. The cleaner, wearing full PPE, demonstrates the effective application of HG Mould Remover foam and spray to clean the affected walls. Following the cleaning, she introduces and installs both electric and classic dehumidifiers, damp-seals the walls and ceilings, and repaints them with anti-mold paint to ensure long-term prevention. The video culminates in a dramatic before-and-after showcasing the complete transformation of the room into a clean and safe environment.",
